      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks for explaining. i guess i'm mostly wondering about the \"concerns\" part. i've heard some people say that parents who are worried about this are just being \"uninformed\" or \"anti-science.\" is that actually a fair way to describe the parents who have issues with the curriculum, or is there more to it than that?",
